p: Herman Tse**#{27}":[46,46],"###**Call Prep: Herman Tse**#{28}":[47,47],"###**Call Prep: Herman Tse**#{29}":[48,48],"###**Call Prep: Herman Tse**#{30}":[49,49],"###**Call Prep: Herman Tse**#{31}":[50,50],"###**Call Prep: Herman Tse**#{32}":[51,51],"###**Call Prep: Herman Tse**#{33}":[52,52],"###**Call Prep: Herman Tse**#{34}":[53,53],"###**Call Prep: Herman Tse**#{35}":[54,62],"#key_language: Any transformation in his eyes needs to be evidence based. However the GM's he talks to and other stakeholders are either too risk averse, or a structure / leadership change just changes things without much consideration.":[63,63],"#messy_problem: Speed to get the foundation data gathering and testing for decisions on big investments. The leaders don't want to wait that long.":[64,64],"#messy_problem: Cultural - organisations don't understand what AI is. they struggle to utilize it appropriately.":[65,65],"#messy_problem: Cyber Risk - Clients often don't understand just how vulnerable their data is. it only takes a few prompts and he can hack into an LLM and get the data.":[66,66],"#messy_problem: Media spreading anti-AI rumours which causes issues":[67,67],"#action_item: Book in more time with Anthony to stay in touch. he wants me to join Student alumni events, possibly go down to Melbourne":[68,68],"#action_item: Read Anthony's papers.":[69,69],"#action_item: potentially write a paper in collaboration with Anthony":[70,70]},"outlinks":[],"metadata":{"tags":["#1-2","#messy_problem","#action_item"]},"task_lines":[],"last_embed":{"hash":"18bvt9y","at":1762219138585}},"smart_blocks:docs/Stakeholder Engagment/C1 - Herman Tse/C1 - Herman Tse Call Notes.md###**Call Prep: Herman Tse**": {"path":null,"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.06155368,-0.01378516,-0.0006842,-0.07062576,0.00030091,0.01360511,0.0381162,0.07758346,0.02315679,-0.0523975,0.01979689,-0.00715839,0.01125654,-0.00899551,0.03271607,0.02650598,-0.03506656,0.00685776,-0.00729724,0.02453752,0.01406945,-0.0