p: Herman Tse**#{27}":[46,46],"###**Call Prep: Herman Tse**#{28}":[47,47],"###**Call Prep: Herman Tse**#{29}":[48,48],"###**Call Prep: Herman Tse**#{30}":[49,49],"###**Call Prep: Herman Tse**#{31}":[50,50],"###**Call Prep: Herman Tse**#{32}":[51,51],"###**Call Prep: Herman Tse**#{33}":[52,52],"###**Call Prep: Herman Tse**#{34}":[53,53],"###**Call Prep: Herman Tse**#{35}":[54,62],"#key_language: Any transformation in his eyes needs to be evidence based. However the GM's he talks to and other stakeholders are either too risk averse, or a structure / leadership change just changes things without much consideration.":[63,63],"#messy_problem: Speed to get the foundation data gathering and testing for decisions on big investments. The leaders don't want to wait that long.":[64,64],"#messy_problem: Cultural - organisations don't understand what AI is. they struggle to utilize it appropriately.":[65,65],"#messy_problem: Cyber Risk - Clients often don't understand just how vulnerable their data is. it only takes a few prompts and he can hack into an LLM and get the data.":[66,66],"#messy_problem: Media spreading anti-AI rumours which causes issues":[67,67],"#action_item: Book in more time with Anthony to stay in touch. he wants me to join Student alumni events, possibly go down to Melbourne":[68,68],"#action_item: Read Herman's papers.":[69,69],"#action_item: Research ways to automate the research and data gathering for the discovery phase of projects":[70,70]},"outlinks":[],"metadata":{"tags":["#1-2","#messy_problem","#action_item"]},"task_lines":[],"last_embed":{"hash":"1mtl2u3","at":1762219305248}},"smart_blocks:docs/Stakeholder Engagment/C1 - Herman Tse/C1 - Herman Tse Call Notes.md###**Call Prep: Herman Tse**": {"path":null,"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.06201244,-0.01422671,-0.00075771,-0.07069895,0.00043035,0.01376309,0.03814254,0.07745241,0.02296525,-0.05214694,0.02044437,-0.00705461,0.01097497,-0.00870545,0.03262266,0.02650452,-0.03493183,0.0070009